reviewText: A glorious cheese fest remake of the anime, less of a remake of the game.
Follower the anime pretry closely it looked a lititle bad sometimes but for the most part it was a really good asian horror movie I liked it more than I though I would honestly
Follows the game pretty well for the most part.

This movie more or less followed the anime adaptation of Corpse Party. The movie itself was a good adaptation, and is a good story all on its own. The graphics and acting were cheesy at times. That being said, if you love Corpse Party the anime (or game) this is definitely worth a watch.
